{"tid":90191,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"外國有條友將自己鎖左係間隔離房三日","createTime":"2017-01-22T00:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T16:54:40.000Z","uid":54344,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28e5f315ff636a3e202952d3a3e3d6dacb1d959e","tid":90191,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T00:32:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iqKdEhx-dD4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiqKdEhx-dD4&d=pjepta7IDo9He3ZZvGfzZ5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e954d656\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iqKdEhx-dD4</a><br />\n<br />\nWhat happens when your brain is deprived of stimulation? What effect does being cut off from interaction with the outside world have on a person? What effect does it have on me, when I am locked in a windowless, soundproof isolation chamber for three days? In this episode of Mind Field, I take both an objective and a very intimate look at Isolation. <br />\n<br />\n當你的大腦被剝奪觀感刺激時會發生什麼？ 當一個人與外部世界的互動被切斷時，又會有什麼效果？ 當我被鎖在一個無窗、隔音隔離室三天，它對我有什麼影響？"},{"pid":"dc7fd65dcdebac3591fdaa39bdfece7cd9cfef5c","tid":90191,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T00:33:06.000Z","msg":"between, 有中文字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a6dbed7462c838fc0a6451551f2fb6f45bf055","tid":90191,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T00:46:29.000Z","msg":"唔出膠post就冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02cda3b5e8b9163bb9571c8fe903e70d69487cd","tid":90191,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:05:22.000Z","msg":"幾正，如果係我應該半日就發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca4f74eb8f3dedf9aa64e7213e393c21224beaa","tid":90191,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score